13:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Mutable AI and Snyk Code AI share a solid foundation of core features including Multi Language. Where Mutable AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Code Generation and Refactoring and Chat and Documentation, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Snyk Code AI uniquely offers Code Review and Debugging and Ide Integration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Mutable AI holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Snyk Code AI scores 8/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
14:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Mutable AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $12/mo, compared to Snyk Code AI's starting price of $25/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Mutable AI's free tier and Snyk Code AI's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
