ale"]}],["$","li","2",{"style":{"color":"var(--text-secondary)"},"children":[["$","span",null,{"style":{"position":"absolute","left":0,"color":"var(--red)","fontWeight":700},"children":"-"}],"Can be slow on large repos"]}]]}]]}]]}]
17:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Mutable AI is best suited for auto generating documentation, codebase understanding, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Snyk Code AI, meanwhile, shines for security focused teams, vulnerability detection, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2021, Mutable AI describes itself as \"AI-accelerated software development and documentation.\" Snyk Code AI, established in 2015, positions itself as \"AI-powered security scanning for your code.\" With 6 years between them, Snyk Code AI brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Mutable AI offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
18:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Snyk Code AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 6.0), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Mutable AI is a poor choice — far from it. Mutable AI excels in its own right, particularly for auto generating documentation and codebase understanding.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value industry-leading security scanning, go with Snyk Code AI. If auto-generates wiki from code matters more to you, Mutable AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
